 \det A = \sum_\sigma {\epsilon(\sigma)} \prod_i A_{i,\sigma (i)}\\ \det A^T = \sum_\sigma {\epsilon(\sigma)} \prod_i A_{\sigma (i),i} \\\forall\sigma\ \  \prod_i A_{\sigma(i),i} = \prod_j A_{j,\sigma^{-1}(j)} 
